{"id":"jeush","term":"Jeush","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Assembler. (1.) The oldest of Esau’s three sons by Aholibamah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:5\">Gen. 36:5</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:14\">14</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:18\">18</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A son of Bilhan, grandson of Benjamin (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 7:10\">1 Chr. 7:10</a>).</p>\n<p>(3.) A Levite, one of the sons of Shimei (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 23:10\">1 Chr. 23:10</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 23:11\">11</a>).</p>\n<p>(4.) One of the three sons of Rehoboam (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 11:19\">2 Chr. 11:19</a>).</p>\n<p>(5.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 8:39\">1 Chr. 8:39</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:5","Genesis 36:14","Genesis 36:18","1 Chronicles 7:10","1 Chronicles 23:10","1 Chronicles 23:11","2 Chronicles 11:19","1 Chronicles 8:39"]}